  stimulus_text = 'The following sentence is punctuated incorrectly. Which choice correctly punctuates the sentence? The dog wagged its tail, happy to see its owner, its excitement was obvious. Researchers note that the pattern described above remained consistent across repeated observations, suggesting the finding was not a one-time anomaly. They caution that local conditions can still vary, yet the overall relationship held in each documented case.',
